  "texts": [
    "A full breakdown of CLEAR, chunk embedding, and full-note performance per variable is reported in Supplementary Table 6.",
    "We used CLEAR to label a dataset to fine-tune a Bio+Clinical BERT for information extraction of the 13 variables in the Stanford MOUD dataset and 5 variables in the CheXpert dataset.",
    "Within the 13 Stanford MOUD Dataset classifiers, two showed perfect discrimination on the test set (AUC = 1).",
    "The \"suicidal behavior\" classifier had the lowest AUC (0.83).",
    "Within the CheXpert Dataset, the \"cardiomegaly\" classifier had the highest AUC (AUC = 1), and the \"pulmonary edema\" classifier had the lowest AUC (AUC = 0.97) (Supplementary Table 7)."
  ],
